For \code{prob = 'posterior'}, \eqn{g_{\mathrm{Go},i}} is evaluated at
\code{theta.TV} and \eqn{g_{\mathrm{NoGo},i}} at \code{theta.MAV}.  For
\code{prob = 'predictive'}, both use \code{theta.NULL} with opposite tail
directions.
